Description: Chert bangle: with rounded profile and slightly convex inner face. There are no breaks in the circumference.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: W. M. F. Petrie, ‘Diospolis Parva: the Cemeteries of Abadiyeh and Hu. 1898-9’ (London, 1901), 36; pl. VII.
Bibliographic references: Andrews 1981 / Catalogue of Egyptian Antiquities. Jewellery I (164)
